1
00:00:00,400 --> 00:00:04,500
FROM ID COACH TO COACHFACE™

2
00:00:04,700 --> 00:00:09,600
In 2009, inventor and entrepreneur Isaac Daniel introduced ID Coach in Tampa, Florida.

3
00:00:09,900 --> 00:00:14,600
During Super Bowl week, athletes, coaches, media and football executives witnessed the future.

4
00:00:14,900 --> 00:00:19,500
The system securely transmitted play calls directly from coaches to designated players.

5
00:00:19,800 --> 00:00:24,300
Military-grade encryption replaced hand signals and traditional audio transmitters.

6
00:00:24,600 --> 00:00:29,400
Strategic decisions could move instantly and securely during competition.

7
00:00:29,700 --> 00:00:34,500
The technology was futuristic. The sports world was not yet ready.

8
00:00:34,800 --> 00:00:39,400
But the vision endured: better tools, better decisions, better performance.

9
00:00:39,700 --> 00:00:44,300
More than fifteen years later, that vision has evolved.

10
00:00:44,600 --> 00:00:49,300
CoachFace™ measures coaching intelligence, accountability and performance.

11
00:00:49,600 --> 00:00:54,300
Fans can evaluate, predict, rank and challenge the decisions that shape sports.

12
00:00:54,600 --> 00:00:59,900
IF FANS KNOW WHAT COACHES SHOULD DO, CAN THEY OUTPERFORM THEM?